Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:05.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is male, and represents a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:08.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And the moon is female; representing a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:13.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,When the sun and the moon come together, they become one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:16.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...in other words, it represents a perfect being.{ok LOL}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:20.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,When they say "perfect being", are they talking about immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is that it's something even more incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:25.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:29.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like... God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:35.55,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:40.01,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I shall no longer be chained down by You!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:45.73,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I shall drag You down to earth and make You a part of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:42.12,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.04,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.62,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,A job well done, my dear sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.55,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So you actually did it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:58.63,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've obtained God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,'God', you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:01.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the bullshit-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.68,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.35,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in possession of a tremendous amount of energy, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean, everyone has already been turned into a philosopher's stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.24,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many lives were lost...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There are roughly 50 million people in this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:31.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:35.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.84,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I've sealed off alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.93,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.47,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.52,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've devoured God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.98,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,it's not impossible for me to create a sun in the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.28,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Should I let this loose right here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:11.08,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The turnabout had already begun from the moment you were in possession of Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:21.59,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,For this day and for this day only,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:25.93,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I had positioned my friends,\Nmy philosopher's stones, all across the nation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.39,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,...over a long period of time and with many calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.69,Default,Stone,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:41.45,Default,Stone,0000,0000,0000,,He did something he shouldn't have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.45,Default,Stone,0000,0000,0000,,We no longer have a body to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:49.95,Default,Stone,0000,0000,0000,,However, the people of Amestris do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:55.71,Default,Stone,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Let us return their souls to their respective bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.96,Default,Stone,0000,0000,0000,,Hohenheim asked us to, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.80,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,So all you did was to implant your philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.85,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,But those are just points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.47,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Without a circle, there is no alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.47,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,That's a basic principle of alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.56,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But there IS a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:20.99,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,A huge, powerful circle that'll activate by itself even if something were to happen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.12,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow of the moon that occurs from the solar eclipse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:31.75,Default,Stone,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going on ahead, Hohenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.76,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You just continue to get in my way,\Ndon't you, Hohenheim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.43,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely what I came here to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.76,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Dwarf in the Flask, Homunculus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.35,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Winry... are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.81,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What... just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did we lose consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.03,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,It happened to you two as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.86,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.45,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,How can I explain it... it was as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:39.37,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like I was drowning in a whirlpool of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.38,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:49.59,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,The souls of the people of Amestris were returned to their respective bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:57.31,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be able to restrain this being he calls 'God' with only the souls of the people of Xerxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.11,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I can just create another philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.07,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred million, or even a billion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.49,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Humans, an energy form, are an unlimited source!{wow, disobeying the law of economics}{you are a dumb nigger}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:29.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:35.43,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,It's as easy as pie for an Eastern Alchemist to read and utilize the flow of the earth's energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:41.31,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,The more power he has, the more power we have that we can use as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.90,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.82,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.28,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough time to offset the energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.70,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.37,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,The defense circle will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.46,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.42,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Stand firm, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, don't you dare give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.26,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.81,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a terrible father, but I want to make you two proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry up, the philosopher's stone inside of Dad will run out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.99,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Ishbalan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.87,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that alchemy, the reconstruction of matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:43.96,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,was a sin against Ishvala, the creator of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.34,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Have you abandoned your god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:59.01,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.10,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,...'God' is hardly significant to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.23,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Nay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:10.69,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,After you learned the true meaning of despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.82,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,...during the Ishbalan War...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.71,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,You must have realized somewhere inside of your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.71,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,God does not exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:08.21,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in neither destiny nor a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:14.00,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,but one would probably look at this situation and say that the heavens are not on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.47,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,The heavens brought forth a fitting visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.35,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here to avenge your grandfather...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.98,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.65,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:34.98,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.78,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,A sad life you led.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:43.58,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,King Bradley, was there no one you loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.54,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? Your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.46,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Wife, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.96,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,You have no words to pass on to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.71,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,If she found out that you were a homunculus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:59.42,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, quit blabbering on about trifling topics such as love and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.55,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.51,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,She's the woman I chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:09.98,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,A will is unnecessary between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.77,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,That's usually how it is between a King and his companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:24.74,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you missed the chance to take revenge as you were caught up in foolish dialogue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:36.17,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Although my life was lived atop a rail which was already prepared for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.97,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:48.02,Default,Brad,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel like my life was somewhat worthwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.78,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,A sign of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.07,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It's a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.24,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.08,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.17,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me to that spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.96,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,The transmutation circle is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.26,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.93,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,That's the center of it all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:23.84,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:37.11,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Dear brother, to tell you the truth, I am not completely rid of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:42.74,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, I'm currently trying to help the ones\Nwhom my hatred is directed at: the Amestrians.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:47.74,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You once related it to the flow of positives and negatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.91,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,but where will I, who carry both of those conflicting elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.67,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,be carried off to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.18,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:33.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That chair you've been sitting high and mighty on is now in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:38.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You've had your share of fun for your lifetime, bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat the shit out of both you and Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.85,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... Eastern Alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.52,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's something my brother invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.40,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,He used to research alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:06.53,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,And from there, he began to research Eastern Alchemy from Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:11.53,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Alchemy utilizes the flow of earth's energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.83,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy from Amestris utilizes tectonic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.54,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,But my brother realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.88,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,...that alchemists are unable to use all of that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:30.93,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in the way between the alchemist and the tectonic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:34.22,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling I got when I first came to this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:38.39,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,...it felt as though there were people crawling about underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.15,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:45.86,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the philosopher's stones that were stretched across underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:15:00.04,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,So Sir, the purpose of your transmutation circle was to return everyone's souls to their bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.88,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:09.38,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,And the purpose of the Turnabout Transmutation Circle Scar activated was to fix this nation's alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:16.18,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,After extensive research, Scar's brother began to doubt this nation's alchemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:20.69,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,and additionally, learned of the existence of the Nationwide Transmutation Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.65,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,And with that at its base, and utilizing Eastern Alchemy for inscription,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:30.53,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,he created the Turnabout Transmutation Circle; one that would nullify the power of a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:36.28,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,And with this, alchemists are able to use all the tectonic energy to their liking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.95,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,something that used to be disrupted by philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.80,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.18,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Make him use his philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.39,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,He'll eventually run out of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And when'll that be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.47,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.31,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But all we can do is try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.77,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.11,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.53,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I remember bathing in that once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.24,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a soak too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way, Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.85,Default,Bri,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.52,Default,Bri,0000,0000,0000,,Now, slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.40,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hawkeye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.65,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:03.25,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,He must have gone up to create more philosopher's stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.59,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We're going after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.38,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get you somewhere safe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so useless when people need me the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he wants a piece of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.40,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die now, Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yes'm!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.20,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.62,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.83,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.87,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:48.88,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.13,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:56.13,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone that needs a real good spanking, so I'll be off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.30,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Are you injured, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,They took my vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What about your wounds, Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.60,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.81,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Please worry about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:11.27,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.03,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:18.91,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.12,Default,Lan,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.21,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,It's Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.13,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you followed us all the way down-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.59,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.60,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,So he bit the dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.23,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You look so damn satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.44,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.02,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Greed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.73,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing away his pride as a homunculus... how pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:59.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys so obedient towards a father like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.32,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.83,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious that we'd obey our own father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're the stupid one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Obvious" you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:14.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even try thinking with your own brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you continue to obey him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:28.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't give a damn even if you're badly hurt like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:33.90,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:39.86,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apply this "common knowledge" of your human race to us homunculi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.00,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,This container won't last for very much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:55.54,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,But since you, like our father,\Nhave Hohenheim's blood in your veins,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.50,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,we're pretty much siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:01.55,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric, give me your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.34,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,...a container!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.43,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.10,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Unamused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.98,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thoroughly unamused, homunculus Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.61,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee?! There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:24.24,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,How could you maintain your own self-awareness in this tempest of souls...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.45,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.41,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You make me giggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.87,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Voices of resentment are like a lullaby to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.21,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you interfering with me, Kimblee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:45.34,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't have done anything had you kept on fighting while conserving your pride as a homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:49.85,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,However, first, you blab on about your pride as a homunculus,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.98,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,then just as your life is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:58.31,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,you proceed to escape into the container of a human, a being you looked down on as inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:20:59.23,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.48,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...lack elegance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:11.54,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.67,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Selim!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.55,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:31.64,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,He turned himself into a philosopher's stone to infiltrate me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you now, Selim!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.27,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.11,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:47.61,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:14.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go and apologize to Madam Bradley after all this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:18.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait there, stupid brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:27.36,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy... Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.54,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,The strong arms roars; the flame thunders forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:06.54,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Staking their existence, the people give their full measure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:10.80,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The final battle is now here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.51,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:19.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 62, A Fierce Counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:24.74,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If one wishes to gain something,\None must present something of equal value.
